targets.query:
from(bucket: "HomeServer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "cpu")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "usage_user")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["cpu"] == "cpu-total")
  |> group(columns: ["cpu"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "HomeServer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_cpu")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "usage_percent")
  |> group(columns: ["_measurement", "_field", "container_image"])
  |> last()
  |> group(columns: ["com.docker.compose.project"])
  |> sum()
  |> keep(columns: ["com.docker.compose.project", "_value"])
  |> rename(columns: {"_value": ""})
  |> yield()

from(bucket: "HomeServer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "mem")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "used")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "HomeServer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_mem")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "usage")
  |> group(columns: ["_measurement", "_field", "container_image"])
  |> last()
  |> group(columns: ["_measurement", "_field", "com.docker.compose.project"])
  |> sum()
  |> keep(columns: ["com.docker.compose.project", "container_image", "_value"])
  |> rename(columns: {"_value": ""})
  |> yield()

from(bucket: "HomeServer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "net")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "bytes_sent")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["host"] == "HOME-Server")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["interface"] == "enp1s0")
  |> group(columns: ["interface"])
  |> derivative(unit: 1s, nonNegative: true)
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: sum, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "sent")

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["com.docker.compose.project"] == "wordpress")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_start", "_stop", "com.docker.compose.service", "_value"])
  |> rename(columns: {"com.docker.compose.service": "Container"})
  |> yield(name: "mean")
